Programs for Computational Biology Course:

-CoupledHarmonicOscillators

Simulates N coupled quantum harmonic oscillators. Entropy and energy distribution estimations.

-IdealGasEnergy

Simulates N quantum ideal Gas particles in 3D by the "Maxwell Demon" algorithm. Energy distribution estimation.

-velocityVerlteSho

Molecular Dynamics simulation of a single classical harmonic oscillator with the velocity verlet algorithm.

Prerequisites (linux):

g++
gcc
make
gsl (GNU scientific library)

For compilation instructions, in each program directory type (in Ubuntu and derivatives):

$sudo apt-get install libgsl-dev g++ gcc make libboost-all-dev

$ make

In each documentation directory you will find usage instructions.
